14 impact zone to coordinate with the United States department of defense military
15 aviation and installation assurance siting clearinghouse for zoning, land use,
16 construction, energy development, telecommunications, and other infrastructure
17 projects that could impact military rada r , airspace, communications, or
18 operational readiness.
